dct_description_sm: Engraved by the Topographic Eng. Co., Washington, D.C. ; litho. A. Hoen & Co. Balto. Md.--Lower margin.; Includes lists of railroads showing miles, state institutions, state parks, and Indian reservations. Also includes statistical tables and list of counties giving area, population, county seat, distance from Madison, and distance from Milwaukee.; Includes index to cities, villages and other places.; Insets: Duluth/Superior -- Milwaukee.
99 x 85 centimeters, on sheet 134 x 91 centimeters
